[{"id":575735,"node":"推广","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/promotions","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1fc2/1400/864_mini.png?m=1497247521","description":"<p>去年这个时候在 V2 上做过分享，讲述我离开北京后回家从事水产的一些。<a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/461597#reply59\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/461597#reply59</a></p>\n<p>去年 10 月份，大闸蟹季节开始的时候 我又重新梳理了一遍这一年以来的心路历程，原本计划向各位 V 友同步进展，文章没能发出来。最后同步在公号 <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/v96BhQMgOAEhdcSm3kV8kw\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/v96BhQMgOAEhdcSm3kV8kw</a></p>\n<p>17 年 8 月份离开北京，一直从事水产。交了很多学费，趟了很多坑，也遭受了很多压力。这些压力不是来自经济上、生活上，而是来自父老乡亲、来自七大姑八大姨。</p>\n<p>我姑父对我爸说“没想到国栋混成这个样（指我回农村从事农业相关）”</p>\n<p>我姐偶尔发牢骚“别人家舅舅读完书在外面上班，就你回来搞农活，这都是农憨子干的事，你有时要为我们考虑下，我们说出去都不好听”</p>\n<p>我妈在外面听见邻里讨论后，会对我大发脾气。</p>\n<p>我在朋友圈分享一些村里劳作的照片和视频，隔壁的叔叔会留言“年轻人还是应该出来多闯闯”</p>\n<p>有时我姨会安慰我：尽管可能当下面子上不好看，如果能混出个名堂来，别人自然会改变看法。</p>\n<p>前几天在朋友圈里分享我最近一次因大姐埋怨我在家干农活与大姐吵架的经历，有个之前在实现网工作期间认识的开发者评论道：对于我的遭遇，他也身同感受。背景是 14 年前后他从大厂离职，做起了自由职业者，几年下来，也面临这样的困境</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/a45b8db5gy1g47e6bjfgpj20u01hc44g.jpg\" alt=\"此处输入图片的描述\"></p>\n<p>我回复：你在北京，好歹不在亲戚眼皮子底下，我这每天在村里来来回回，压力不一样。</p>\n<p>两年来，往返了很多地方，泰州兴化、南京高淳、深圳布吉、武汉白沙洲、洪湖、、潜江、郑州、石家庄、大同、北京，寻找货源、寻找客商、送货、接货、卖货。一路跌跌撞撞，好在非常充实，一年比一年有奔头。</p>\n<p>如果按年头算，今年算第三个年头了。</p>\n<p>做了两年的探索，今年试图将鲜活小龙虾做成成品，即加热即食。花了几个月的时间准备资质，跑工厂，原本计划五一上市，结果因为各种情况在 6 月 2 号前后才得以上市。很多朋友留言说我这条路走对了。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/a45b8db5gy1g47ew1h4edj20qz1c9416.jpg\" alt=\"此处输入链接的描述\"></p>\n<p>半个月时间，卖了大概两百份，总体看，味道一致比较认可。有一部分朋友有两次和三次以上的复购。</p>\n<p>之前在实现网的合伙人龙行同学，给 6 个亲戚朋友送了，一向很少发朋友圈的他，深夜发了个硬广推荐。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw1024/a45b8db5gy1g47fbopi61j20u01hcq7k.jpg\" alt=\"此处输入链接的描述\"></p>\n<p>V 友，最近如有采购计划，希望可以联系我。因与工厂的合作有起订量的要求。故这一批次生产的比较多。目前冷库里还有满满一冷库。压力有点大。期待得到大家的支持！感谢</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575735","replies":108,"created_ts":1560999406,"created":"10:56:46","title":"那个北漂 8 年，返乡卖小龙虾的又来了","author":"olollo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/olollo","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/47cc/47e8/201504_mini.png?m=1497159699"},{"id":575708,"node":"生活方式","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/lifestyle","node_image":"/static/img/node_mini.png","description":"<p>从灵魂深处是真的不想熬夜，熬夜太伤皮肤了，什么兰蔻雅诗兰黛都白用，那都是大洋呀，关键是熬夜第二天没精神还易猝死！！！\n但是每天晚上回到家，洗完澡吹完头发都要十点多了，立马睡觉就感觉今天一天白过一样，还想再看会书追会剧，然而一旦开始就停不下来，就要到一点，第二天早上又开始后悔，每天都是这样的死循环。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575708","replies":104,"created_ts":1560995985,"created":"09:59:45","title":"如何避免熬夜呢？每日都在思考","author":"NoSugarTea","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/NoSugarTea","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1ddb7179d42c09c53ece00aed834c45c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":575720,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1561032025","description":"实习期, 近来发现公司好多 PC 是 WIN7 环境, 这一点我不能理解(我是 Ubuntu), win10 已经发布好几年了 ,  为什么还有那么多坚持 win7 的？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575720","replies":103,"created_ts":1560997230,"created":"10:20:30","title":"（闲谈）关于生产环境中坚持 win7 开发的疑惑","author":"Northxw","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Northxw","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dc37247953bb8729158198bf203930f4?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":575779,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1561032025","description":"ubuntu 很好，不过没有很多工具，比如 ssr 客户端，浏览器也看不了 youtube,有没有好的选项，今天试一下 deepin,安装不到 u 盘里，很失望😔","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575779","replies":102,"created_ts":1561003678,"created":"12:07:58","title":"国内开发用什么版本 Linux 最舒服","author":"daijinming","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/daijinming","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4f11/50e7/286504_mini.png?m=1536223283"},{"id":575744,"node":"健康","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/fit","node_image":"/static/img/node_mini.png","description":"有没有感同身受的 v2er，这玩意跟大姨妈似的每个月总有那么几天，疼的吃不下饭、说不了话。什么金喉健喷雾、西瓜霜、B2、蜂胶贴、什么意可贴、还有什么膜都用过","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575744","replies":78,"created_ts":1561000145,"created":"11:09:05","title":"口腔溃疡有没有什么比较好用的药","author":"lockltd","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lockltd","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c288a736d3b648c02fd9570610f17424?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":575655,"node":"全球工单系统","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/gts","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/74bb/a227/938_mini.png?m=1550427791","description":"因为日常用 Ubuntu，为了 Office 体验以及云同步选了腾讯微云。最近一个月一直在微云上写，结果今晚就发现文档打不开了？？？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575655","replies":78,"created_ts":1560960952,"created":"00:15:52","title":"腾讯微云放着的毕业论文打不开了，下载的话显示一个一个月前的版本","author":"lance6716","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lance6716","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/965c/95a3/64495_mini.png?m=1531304075"},{"id":575748,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1559643304","description":"<p>上次谢谢各位 V 友鼎力相助，最终决定选择平层。<br>\n因为上次那两个户型缺点明显<br>\n这周又看了几个平层，挑一个比较有代表性的跟大家分享下，看看大家意见：<br></p>\n<h2>户型一 160㎡  电梯-两梯两户  价格贵 30%</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://mall.mouseover.cn/111.png\" alt=\"image\">\n<br><br></p>\n<h2>户型一 150㎡  电梯-两梯四户</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://mall.mouseover.cn/222.png\" alt=\"image\"></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575748","replies":68,"created_ts":1561000312,"created":"11:11:52","title":"继续发两个户型，大家帮给点意见","author":"miao666","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/miao666","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/78d9b7a74ad092e8547a98a4f7eb6dbb?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":575858,"node":"健康","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/fit","node_image":"/static/img/node_mini.png","description":"<p>大学的时候坚持跑了三个月，减了 25 斤吧，肥膘都没了感觉很爽。然后平稳保持了两年跑步习惯。</p>\n<p>今年也才 25，这肚子又起来了，很不爽。</p>\n<p>两年间立 FLAG 要重新开始跑步立了不下五次吧，每次坚持不到一个月就 GG。</p>\n<p>每次刚开始 4KM，要结束的时候 2KM，最后没了。</p>\n<p>昨晚又开始了，怕又坚持不下去，很慌。</p>\n<p>感觉自己找的坚持跑步的理由分分钟被自己抛弃。。。</p>\n<p>咋办，这可咋整。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575858","replies":64,"created_ts":1561016217,"created":"15:36:57","title":"到底怎么样才能坚持长期跑步？","author":"Vendettar","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Vendettar","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/34a102fa4d2bf297c79083d2e74105a1?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":575828,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1561032025","description":"<p>在 SRE 的世界里，有个概念叫做“事后无过失”（ blameless postmortem ），这是一种回顾过去所犯错误的方式，但不会将责任归咎于任何人。在谷歌工作了近 5 年的隐私工程师塔里克·尤素福(Tariq Yusuf)表示：“这是谷歌文化的一个基本组成部分，也是让人能够大胆剖析出问题的能力。但报复消除了能够安全提出问题的核心阻碍，整个过程因此而崩溃。”</p>\n<p>———— <a href=\"https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/859031.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/859031.htm</a> 谷歌\"内战\"：高管要利润，员工要价值观，谁是灵魂？</p>\n<p>大部分公司应该都会追责吧 即使没有相关处罚 各种潜在影响（绩效 KPI...）也是避免不了吧 想听听大佬们的意见 也想了解下大厂的处理方式</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575828","replies":63,"created_ts":1561011678,"created":"14:21:18","title":"生产环境故障该不该追责员工","author":"Sothoth","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Sothoth","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0831/6016/372362_mini.png?m=1546046730"},{"id":575701,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1558512651","description":"<p>作为一名星爷的脑残粉，见证了太多的经典台词，所以一直想做一个与台词有关的东西。终于这次开发了这一款小程序，专门用来收集影片中的经典台词，取名为 \"小台词\"。里面的每句台词都是重看影片证实取得的，包括台词的出处和哪个演员角色说的。</p>\n<p>这是一款自己真心喜欢的作品，不过目前台词库还很不完善，接下来也会持续丰富，包括优化小程序功能和体验，喜欢台词感兴趣的同学也可以提一些你们的宝贵意见。下面是其中一些台词截图。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-11-18-435_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-11-27-152_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-11-36-120_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-11-41-995_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-11-55-155_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-12-28-845_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-12-39-783_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-12-55-631_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-13-02-933_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://actline.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/tuiguang/Screenshot_2019-06-20-09-13-14-022_%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1.png?x-oss-process=image/auto-orient,1/resize,p_40/quality,q_90\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>这是小程序码</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/wxopen/qrcode?action=show&amp;type=2&amp;fakeid=3507259818&amp;token=1538034769\" alt=\"\"></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575701","replies":60,"created_ts":1560995225,"created":"09:47:05","title":"又一个小程序","author":"awesomes","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/awesomes","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cb44/483e/135006_mini.png?m=1560995176"},{"id":576011,"node":"Android","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/android","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1561032004","description":"从 Pixel 2 升级过来的，屏幕真的真的好长啊 lol<br />大家有什么想要了解的吗？(｀･ω･´)","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/576011","replies":54,"cr