哪些词汇合适，欢迎添加 PR 来贡献！</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/575682","replies":48,"created_ts":1560992206,"created":"08:56:46","title":"在美国大公司工作若干年，分享下自己平时积累的英语词汇。","author":"xw900812","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xw900812","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4974f9621919eca1378752cc1347508b?s=24&d=retro"}]